<![CDATA[<p class="MsoNormal" style=""><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><span style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; line-height: 17.12px; background: white;">Hi {!Lead.FirstName},<br></span><br>I’ve been unable to reach you since you provided your details via our Facebook form.<br><br>This means I’ve been unable to provide you with the business insurance quote you requested.<br><br></font><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">If you are&nbsp;</span><b style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">interested in proceeding with your quote</b><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">, just let me know the best date and time for me to call you. Alternatively you can give me a ring on&nbsp;</span><b style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">01242 808 740</b><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif">.</font></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br>Kind regards,<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br>{!User.FirstName}&nbsp;<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">Sales Team<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br>E: salesteam@kingsbridge.co.uk<br></span><font style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">T:&nbsp;</font><font style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">01242 808740</font></p>]]></td>
